column10:
There is absolutely ZERO reasons for you to play this game... but wait let me explain why:
-The UI looks like it came out from a mobile game, probably one or even the worst i've ever seen; 
-The tutorial is inexistent;
-Progressing without paying feels like a waste of time (no paying means losing your social life alongside 4-5 years of time wasted, but if you pay maybe its gonna take like 2 years... maybe)
-forced pvp even tho its not that huge of a problem, just git gud i guess;
-the game feels like a mix of the most famous mmorpgs out there but making a mess out of it, everything feels pointless and unfinished like some mechanics that have been completely abandoned.

The only pro i give to this game is the combat and the character customization, one of the best i've ever seen... but other than that? the game feels like a big money grabbing machine that gives zero fuck about the community and keeps making pointless update with just more grind and more microtransactions.
Before buying and play this game ask yourself a question... do i have anything else to do in my life? 
Games like this are just a disguised scam, don't fall for it!!

kinda gaming

/kinda not gaming anymore

